====Usage notes====
Often used interchangeably with {{term|機|||tr=[[き]], [[ki]]|lang=ja}} – with same reading き, ''ki'' – in compounds to indicate “machine”, with the subtlety that 器 implies a smaller device, say hand-held, while 機 implies a larger machine, such as an airplane. Compare {{term|食器||tableware|tr=[[しょっき]], [[shokki]]|lang=ja}} with {{term|飛行機||airplane|tr=[[ひこうき]], [[hikōki]]|lang=ja}}

